snippet.title: Gemalomania (SM64 Hack) - The Gem
snippet.description:
Here we are with a level! Livvie has somehow gotten herself in some sort of underground hideout. They must be digging for something. Watch as she passes them Goons and discovers something at the end!

This is a simple preview of the very thing that I wanted to replace: the Star with a Gem! Bacon did a good job helpin' me out with this! I thank em'!

There's still more to do here. And I gotta work on that first world! (and do other things like changing those smaller gems' coloring) See yas soon! I'll update as soon as possible.
